{"sku": "WF0017", "name": "Atlantic Smock - Woolrich x Griffin", "url": "https://www.woolrich.com/atlantic-smock-woolrich-x-griffin-wf0017/", "description": "Woolrich and designer Jeff Griffin of Loveland Farm have teamed up to create a unique capsule collection that combines urban style with technical features. The Atlantic Smock is a fully reversible, unisex piece that transcends gender distinctions. We only made 1830 of this limited-edition style, in honor of the year that Woolrich was founded, and each individually numbered. One side comes in your choice of black or an exclusive photo-print camo produced by Jeff Griffin. The reverse is a combination of blaze orange and The Original Buffalo Check\u2122 plaid, created by Woolrich in 1850, in traditional red and black. Ensuring warmth, it\u2019s down-insulated and features a detachable and reversible coyote fur ruff at the hood with zip- and snap-fastenings. Pullover styling feature button-through closures at the neck on both sides of the garment and a shared side-seam zip-opening. Both sides also share a full kangaroo pocket, with button-through side-entries on the orange and check side and reverse side-entries on the other. Rib-knit storm cuffs hold in heat and a drawcord adjustment at blaze orange side-seam along bottom hem helps lock out cold. Hood has drawcord adjustments on the black or camo side. Orange and check side features the Loveland Farm and Woolrich logos printed on the buffalo check upper back yoke, plus Griffin Studio logo patch on the left sleeve and Woolrich logo patch on the throat latch. This anorak smock comes in our relaxed fit, an easy generous fit that drapes loosely; this unisex garment uses our men\u2019s size chart \u2013 please use the link above the size selection tool to find your correct size.", "categories": ["Home", "Men", "Atlantic Smock - Woolrich x Griffin"], "price": "$1,500.00", "image-urls": ["https://cdn11.bigcommerce.com/s-n29utr4wup/images/stencil/1200x1318/products/1119/1